divs: Sighting DetailsFlying from Pullman Washington to Seattle. Was taking lots of pictures out the plane window. Took several photos of Mt. Rainier to make sure one would be good. Got home to Sacramento that evening and next day downloaded the photos. Noticed the object was in the photo but not in the next shot 10 seconds later. Thought you might want to look at it. Zooming in on the photo it did not appear to be a plane . Photo's included. DSCN 1314 is the first shot with the object in it. DSCN 1315 is the second shot and the object is gone. The time on the photo said PM, but it was really AM. I guess the camera was set wrong.

Summary: Taking photos of Mt. Rainier and did not see object until photos were put on computer the next day.
